%N A209042 Number of n X 3 0..3 arrays with no element equal the average of immediate neighbors vertically above and horizontally left of it.
%C A209042 Column 3 of A209047.
%C A209042 a(n) ~ C*r^n, where r = 36.737973... is the Perron root of the transition matrix, and C = 0.961846... is the asymptotic constant obtained from the Perron projection. - _Adam Reichert_, Jun 12 2026
%H A209042 R. H. Hardin, <a href="/A209042/b209042.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..210</a>
